title: Bloomberg Businessweek Weekend - October 26th, 2019
itunes:title: Bloomberg Businessweek Weekend - October 26th, 2019
description:
Hosted by Carol Massar and Jason Kelly.

Featuring highlights from Bloomberg Businessweek’s special The Year Ahead:

-Mike Regan on how the market will react to the 2020 election cycle

-Lucas Shaw on the 2020 streaming wars

-Craig Giamonna on the American Dream mall opening in New Jersey

-Hannah Elliot on the future of luxury cars

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
